  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个团队工具的工作流图，展示信息是怎么在几个模块之间流转的。起点是聊天室，团队在里面讨论需求。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_ChatRoom"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，聊天室作为入口。那讨论之后，需求会落到哪个工具上？是直接进看板还是先到问题追踪？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_ChatRoom",
        "Groupware_KanbanBoard",
        "Groupware_IssueTracker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "讨论完先落到看板，作为待办项。所以聊天室指向看板，然后看板里的任务如果发现问题，就转到问题追踪器去深入分析。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_ChatRoom",
        "Groupware_KanbanBoard",
        "Groupware_IssueTracker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把这几个节点连起来：聊天室 → 看板 → 问题追踪器。这样对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_ChatRoom",
        "Groupware_KanbanBoard",
        "Groupware_IssueTracker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的。不过问题追踪之后还要有个环节——确认下来的缺陷或者任务要进入迭代待办，也就是Sprint Backlog。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_IssueTracker",
        "Groupware_SprintBacklog"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已加上Sprint Backlog，从问题追踪器连过来。那Sprint Backlog之后呢？开发完成的项怎么处理？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_IssueTracker",
        "Groupware_SprintBacklog"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Sprint Backlog里的任务做完后，要回到看板去展示完成状态，或者进入下一阶段的流程。所以最后一个箭头指回看板。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_SprintBacklog",
        "Groupware_KanbanBoard"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成，现在形成闭环了：聊天室 → 看板 → 问题追踪 → Sprint Backlog → 再回到看板。整体是个从左到右的流程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_ChatRoom",
        "Groupware_KanbanBoard",
        "Groupware_IssueTracker",
        "Groupware_SprintBacklog"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，我看一下——这个闭环里看板出现了两次，开头和结尾。会不会让人混淆？要不要区分一下？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_KanbanBoard"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "确实，同一个节点出现两次技术上可以，但语义上容易误解。要不我们理解为看板是同一个实体，只是任务状态在循环？或者您希望拆成'待办看板'和'完成看板'？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_KanbanBoard"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "不用拆，就是同一个看板。任务从讨论进来，经过追踪和迭代，最后回到看板更新状态。这样体现工作流的循环性。保持原样吧。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_KanbanBoard"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认最终结构：五个节点，四个步骤，从左到右流动，最后回到看板形成闭环。方向是LR横向布局。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_ChatRoom",
        "Groupware_KanbanBoard",
        "Groupware_IssueTracker",
        "Groupware_SprintBacklog"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没问题，这个流程准确反映了我们团队的工作方式。可以定稿了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_ChatRoom",
        "Groupware_KanbanBoard",
        "Groupware_IssueTracker",
        "Groupware_SprintBacklog"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
  ],
